### Transaction Journals - HTTP collection for VS Code REST Client
# Replace {{baseUrl}} with `http://localhost:8081` (or your server URL)
# Replace {{token}} with a valid JWT if you test authenticated endpoints

### Create Transaction Journal
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/transaction-journals
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "yayasanId": 1,
  "institutionId": 1,
  "referenceNumber": "REF-2025-001",
  "invoiceNumber": "INV-2025-001",
  "debitAccountId": 1,
  "creditAccountId": 2,
  "amount": 100000,
  "feeAmount": 2000,
  "providerFee": 500,
  "transactionType": "TRF_INT",
  "description": "Test transaction",
  "status": "SUCCESS",
  "systemSource": "CORE"
}

