### ======================================
### NOTES AND DOCUMENTATION
### ======================================

# API Documentation:
# - All endpoints support pagination with page (0-indexed) and size parameters
# - Default sortBy: "id", default sortDirection: "DESC"
# - Available sort fields: id, timestampTxn, referenceNumber, invoiceNumber, amount, etc.
# - Sort directions: ASC or DESC
#
# Response Formats (via format header):
# - standard (default): PageResponse with clean structure
# - jquery-datatable: JQueryDataTableResponse with draw, recordsTotal, recordsFiltered
# - ant-table: AntDesignTableResponse with success, total, current, pageSize
#
# Account Filter Parameters:
# - accountNumber: Case-insensitive LIKE search (partial matching)
# - accountType: EXACT match - values: ASSET, LIABILITY, EQUITY, REVENUE, EXPENSE
# - accountLevel: EXACT match - values: MAIN, SUB, DETAIL
# - sideType: Filter by transaction side - values: credit, debit (only for credit-debit endpoint)
#
# Credit Journals Endpoint (/credit/all):
# - Returns journals where credit account matches the filters
# - Useful for tracking incoming funds/credits
#
# Debit Journals Endpoint (/debit/all):
# - Returns journals where debit account matches the filters
# - Useful for tracking outgoing funds/debits
#
# Credit and Debit Journals Endpoint (/credit-debit/all):
# - Returns journals where either credit OR debit account matches the filters
# - Can be further filtered by sideType parameter
# - Most flexible endpoint for comprehensive journal queries
#
# Authorization:
# - All endpoints require Bearer token authentication
# - Token should be obtained from login endpoint
#
# Example Response (Standard Format):
# {
#   "data": [...],
#   "total": 100,
#   "page": 0,
#   "size": 20,
#   "totalPages": 5,
#   "hasNext": true,
#   "hasPrevious": false
# }
#
# Example Response (jQuery DataTable Format):
# {
#   "draw": 1,
#   "recordsTotal": 100,
#   "recordsFiltered": 100,
#   "data": [...]
# }
#
# Example Response (Ant Design Format):
# {
#   "data": [...],
#   "success": true,
#   "total": 100,
#   "current": 1,
#   "pageSize": 20
# }
